creator: WEMEMOVE AB
descriptionHtml:
Racefox Run: The world's first real-time digital coach for runners.

Racefox uses a chest sensor to see how your body moves, providing in-the-moment feedback for improved performance and reduced injury. Racefox includes a personalized coach who understands your strengths and weaknesses and makes sure each workout takes you closer to your goal. The benefits of Racefox are seen after only four training sessions, no matter if you're a beginner or an experienced runner.

All you need is your phone, headphones and a Polar H10 or Racefox Smartbelt to get started.

Polar H10 customers can download the app and try Racefox for free.

Get more information about hardware requirements at racefox.com.

OVERVIEW

COMPLETE BODY ANALYSIS
Using AI technology, Racefox performs a full-body motion analysis while running to identify areas of improvement.

REAL-TIME AUDIO COACHING
Training with a digital coach offers in-the-moment feedback on form and technique.

CUSTOMIZED TRAINING PLANS
Based on your personal data, Racefox creates training plans to match your goals.

FOCUS ON INJURY PREVENTION
The Racefox full-body analysis looks at frequency, ground contact time, impact, and drag and creates exercises to minimize future injury.

SET YOUR OWN THRESHOLDS
Target your goal by setting thresholds on frequency exercises and drills.

SEE RESULTS
Racefox runners can shave up to 7% off their race times through improvements in form and technique.
Share with friends: You can automatically sync your data with Strava to share the results of your training with others. Racefox data can also be exported manually.

Racefox is a subscription service that includes regular updates and improvements. You can manage your account on Racefox My Pages once you become a customer. For more information visit racefox.com

title: Racefox Run

creator: WEMEMOVE AB
descriptionHtml:
RUN WITH YOUR HEART AND OUR BRAIN
Racefox provides an innovative and unique way of training with real-time voice coaching. All you have to do is to move and the AI coach will follow and guide you.


IT'S A SMARTER AND EASIER WAY TO RUN
Racefox coaches you in personalized heart rate running and effective running technique, with powerful real-time voice feedback. You will be pushing yourself into pulse zones you normally don’t run in. Successfully run intervals that you previously found hard to manage. The coach’s voice guides you throughout the entire session and afterwards you will be able to analyse your performance in the app. Racefox makes it easy to improve your technique and running form, which will show in your results. You will love it!


ALWAYS WITH YOU
The directness of a physical coach and the data of a sports watch. But powered by AI and ready whenever you have time to train.


BASED ON HOW YOU MOVE
Voice coaching that follows your pulse and your movement to ensure a personalized experience in a way you never experienced before.


REAL-TIME COACHING
Real-time running technique tips in your ear. There is no faster way to learn or easier way to get the most out of your training time.
Racefox runners report a 7% improvement in race times.


FOR EVERYONE
For beginners. For the best. For avoiding injuries.
Our unique training sessions are easy to follow and based on scientific insights on how to maximize effects of training.
Regardless of your level. You only need to bring your desire to improve.

All you need is your phone and headphones to try, it’s free. If you have a Polar H10 belt you can in addition get a full body analysis for free. To experience all our training sessions you need a Polar H10 or Racefox Smartbelt. Try it today!

Racefox is a subscription service that includes regular updates and improvements.
